1.1 不区分编辑步骤和核移植步骤 snv ratio

library("ggplot2")
## Warning: 程辑包'ggplot2'是用R版本4.2.1 来建造的
a1 <- read.table("D:/A_helab_work/Pig/final_figure/samples.snv.mutation.txt",header = T)
colnames(a1)[3] <- "Samples"
a1$id <- as.factor(a1$id)
a1$Samples <- as.factor(a1$Samples)
a1$Class <- as.factor(a1$Class)
a1$number <- as.numeric(a1$number)
C1 <- a1[a1$Samples=="WZS666",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="WZS666",][,4])
C2 <- a1[a1$Samples=="F0-669",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="F0-669",][,4])
C3 <- a1[a1$Samples=="WZS659",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="WZS659",][,4])
C4 <- a1[a1$Samples=="F0-657",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="F0-657",][,4])
C5 <- a1[a1$Samples=="WZS681",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="WZS681",][,4])
C6 <- a1[a1$Samples=="05",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="05",][,4])
a1$ratio <- c(C1,C2,C3,C4,C5,C6)
a1$ratio <- as.numeric(a1$ratio)
a1$Samples <- factor(a1$Samples,levels=c("WZS666","F0-669","WZS659","F0-657","WZS681","05"))
p1 <- ggplot(a1, aes(x = Class, y = ratio, fill = Samples)) +
  geom_bar(stat="identity", position=position_dodge(0.9)) +
  ylab("Fraction") + xlab("") +
  scale_fill_manual(labels=c("666", "669", "659","657","681","05"),values=c("#E69F00","#56B4E9","#CC79A7","#F0E442","#0072B2","#999999")) +
  theme_classic()+
  theme(axis.title.x=element_blank(),
        axis.ticks.x=element_blank(),
        axis.line.x =element_blank()) + # 去掉x轴边界
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0,0.3001),expand = c(0,0)) # 去掉与Y轴间隙
p1

ggsave("6个样本的snv_ratio不区分ed和nt.pdf",p1,width=150,height=100,units=c("mm"))

3.1 编辑过程中不同添加物质的区别 Cas9 snv ratio

library(ggplot2)
a1 <- read.table("D:/A_helab_work/Pig/final_figure/samples.cas9.snv.mutation.txt",header = T)
colnames(a1)[3] <- "Samples"
a1$id <- as.factor(a1$id)
a1$Samples <- as.factor(a1$Samples)
a1$Class <- as.factor(a1$Class)
a1$number <- as.numeric(a1$number)
C1 <- a1[a1$Samples=="WZS01853-ZF3_153-Control",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="WZS01853-ZF3_153-Control",][,4])
C2 <- a1[a1$Samples=="WZS14EFO_214-Control",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="WZS14EFO_214-Control",][,4])
C3 <- a1[a1$Samples=="WZS01853-ZF3_153-Cas9",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="WZS01853-ZF3_153-Cas9",][,4])
C4 <- a1[a1$Samples=="WZS14EFO_214-Cas9",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="WZS14EFO_214-Cas9",][,4])
C5 <- a1[a1$Samples=="WZS14EFO_214-Cas9High",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="WZS14EFO_214-Cas9High",][,4])
C6 <- a1[a1$Samples=="WZS14EFO_214-Cas9Low",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="WZS14EFO_214-Cas9Low",][,4])
C7 <- a1[a1$Samples=="WZS01853-ZF3_153-sgRNACas9-KO-",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="WZS01853-ZF3_153-sgRNACas9-KO-",][,4])
C8 <- a1[a1$Samples=="WZS14EFO_214-sgRNACas9-KO-",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="WZS14EFO_214-sgRNACas9-KO-",][,4])
C9 <- a1[a1$Samples=="WZS01853-ZF3_153-GTKOA39",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="WZS01853-ZF3_153-GTKOA39",][,4])
C10 <- a1[a1$Samples=="WZS14EFO_214-GTKO-A10",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="WZS14EFO_214-GTKO-A10",][,4])
C11 <- a1[a1$Samples=="WZS14EFO_214-GTKO-A7",][,4]/sum(a1[a1$Samples=="WZS14EFO_214-GTKO-A7",][,4])
a1$ratio <- c(C1,C2,C3,C4,C5,C6,C7,C8,C9,C10,C11)
a1$ratio <- as.numeric(a1$ratio)
a1$Samples <- factor(a1$Samples,
                     levels=c("WZS01853-ZF3_153-Control","WZS14EFO_214-Control",
